  "content": "\u003cdiv class\u003d\"content-main relative\"\u003e\n \u003ch1 class\u003d\"block text-[4rem] text-[var(--dark)] leading-[4.4rem] font-semibold mb-[5px]\"\u003eB\u0026agrave; Kamala Harris tiết lộ về khả năng t\u0026aacute;i tranh cử Tổng thống Mỹ\u003c/h1\u003e\n \u003cdiv class\u003d\"content-meta flex items-center flex-wrap flex-row text-[1.3rem] leading-[2rem] font-normal text-[#999] truncate h-[30px] mb-[10px] [\u0026amp;\u0026gt;:not(:first-child)]:ml-[25px]\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class\u003d\"flex items-center\"\u003e\n   \u003ca href\u003d\"/bao-vietnamnet-vietnamnet-p23.epi\" class\u003d\"bm-card-source flex items-center shrink-0\" title\u003d\"B\u0026aacute;o VietnamNet\"\u003e\n    \u003cfigure class\u003d\"image opacity-80 w-auto h-[16px]\" style\u003d\"width:56.25px;height:20px\" aria-label\u003d\"Logo nh\u0026agrave; xuất bản\"\u003e\n     \u003cpicture\u003e\n      \u003csource srcset\u003d\"https://photo-baomoi.bmcdn.me/26dc73b3aef047ae1ee1.png\" type\u003d\"image/avif\"\u003e\u003c/source\u003e\n      \u003csource srcset\u003d\"https://photo-baomoi.bmcdn.me/26dc73b3aef047ae1ee1.png\" type\u003d\"image/webp\"\u003e\u003c/source\u003e\n      \u003cimg src\u003d\"https://photo-baomoi.bmcdn.me/26dc73b3aef047ae1ee1.png\" alt\u003d\"B\u0026aacute;o VietnamNet\" width\u003d\"180\" height\u003d\"64\" /\u003e\n     \u003c/picture\u003e\n    \u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\n   \u003cspan\u003e\u003cbutton class\u003d\"relative text-[14px] leading-[normal] font-normal text-center cursor-pointer normal-case border-0 transition-button disabled:shadow-none disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed follow-button flex items-center item-star ml-[10px]\" tabindex\u003d\"0\" type\u003d\"button\" title\u003d\"Theo d\u0026otilde;i \u0026quot;VietnamNet\u0026quot;\" aria-label\u003d\"Button\"\u003e\u003ci class\u003d\"icon inline-block font-[\u0027bm-font-icon\u0027] not-italic font-normal normal-case leading-none antialiased [speak:never] [font-variant:normal] ic-star text-[var(--primary)]\"\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003ctime datetime\u003d\"2025-10-26T00:19:00.000Z\"\u003e14 giờ trước\u003c/time\u003e\n  \u003ca href\u003d\"/kamala-harris-t41456830.epi\" class\u003d\"related inline !text-[#adb5bd] hover:!text-[var(--primary)]\"\u003e5\n   \u003c!-- --\u003e li\u0026ecirc;n quan\u003c/a\u003e\n  \u003ca href\u003d\"/ba-kamala-harris-tiet-lo-ve-kha-nang-tai-tranh-cu-tong-thong-my-r53586330.epi\" class\u003d\"origin item-origin\" target\u003d\"_blank\" rel\u003d\"noopener noreferrer\"\u003e\u003ci class\u003d\"icon inline-block font-[\u0027bm-font-icon\u0027] not-italic font-normal normal-case antialiased [speak:never] [font-variant:normal] ic-copy text-[13px] mr-[5px]\"\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\u003cspan\u003eGốc\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\n \u003c/div\u003e\n \u003ch3 class\u003d\"sapo block text-[2rem] leading-[2.6rem] font-semibold text-[var(--dark)] p-[10px] bg-[#f2f4f5]\"\u003eCựu Ph\u0026oacute; Tổng thống Kamala Harris khẳng định b\u0026agrave; chưa kết th\u0026uacute;c sự nghiệp ch\u0026iacute;nh trị, v\u0026agrave; ho\u0026agrave;n to\u0026agrave;n c\u0026oacute; thể trở th\u0026agrave;nh Tổng thống tiếp theo của nước Mỹ.\u003c/h3\u003e\n \u003cdiv class\u003d\"content-body text-[2rem] leading-[2.6rem] text-black mt-[15px] break-words overflow-hidden [\u0026amp;_h1]:mb-[15px] [\u0026amp;_h2]:mb-[15px] [\u0026amp;_h3]:mb-[15px] [\u0026amp;_h4]:mb-[15px] [\u0026amp;_h5]:mb-[15px] [\u0026amp;_p]:mb-[15px] [\u0026amp;\u0026gt;div]:mb-[15px]\"\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003eTheo Guardian, b\u0026agrave; \u003ca class\u003d\"tag-link\" href\u003d\"/kamala-harris-tag92.epi\"\u003eKamala Harris\u003c/a\u003e ng\u0026agrave;y 25/10 đ\u0026atilde; tiết lộ về khả năng tiếp tục ra tranh cử Tổng thống Mỹ, đồng thời b\u0026agrave;y tỏ sự tin tưởng về khả năng Nh\u0026agrave; Trắng c\u0026oacute; một nh\u0026agrave; l\u0026atilde;nh đạo nữ.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003e\u0026quot;T\u0026ocirc;i vẫn chưa kết th\u0026uacute;c c\u0026ocirc;ng việc ch\u0026iacute;nh trị. T\u0026ocirc;i đ\u0026atilde; sống cả cuộc đời như một người phục vụ nước \u003ca class\u003d\"tag-link\" href\u003d\"/my-tag81.epi\"\u003eMỹ\u003c/a\u003e, điều đ\u0026oacute; nằm trong xương tủy của t\u0026ocirc;i\u0026quot;, b\u0026agrave; Harris n\u0026oacute;i trong cuộc phỏng vấn với BBC.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003eTuy\u0026ecirc;n bố mới nhất của b\u0026agrave; Harris đ\u0026atilde; \u0026aacute;m chỉ việc cựu Ph\u0026oacute; Tổng thống Mỹ c\u0026oacute; thể ra \u003ca class\u003d\"tag-link\" href\u003d\"/bau-cu-tong-thong-my-tag14697.epi\"\u003etranh cử\u003c/a\u003e trong tương lai, bất chấp việc kh\u0026ocirc;ng được đ\u0026aacute;nh gi\u0026aacute; cao trong c\u0026aacute;c cuộc thăm d\u0026ograve;. C\u0026aacute;c kết quả khảo s\u0026aacute;t gần đ\u0026acirc;y đều kh\u0026ocirc;ng đ\u0026aacute;nh gi\u0026aacute; cao việc b\u0026agrave; Harris trở th\u0026agrave;nh ứng vi\u0026ecirc;n của đảng D\u0026acirc;n chủ, thậm ch\u0026iacute; b\u0026agrave; c\u0026ograve;n xếp sau cả diễn vi\u0026ecirc;n Dwayne \u0026quot;the Rock\u0026quot; Johnson.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class\u003d\"image-wrapper relative z-[1] body-image after:absolute after:top-0 after:left-0 after:z-[-1] after:w-full after:h-full after:opacity-40 after:bg-[url(\u0027https://baomoi-static.bmcdn.me/web/styles/img/logo-baomoi-gray.png\u0027)] after:bg-[length:20%_auto] after:bg-[position:center_50%] after:bg-no-repeat after:bg-[#e9ecef]\"\u003e\n   \u003ci class\u003d\"icon font-[\u0027bm-font-icon\u0027] not-italic font-normal normal-case leading-none antialiased [speak:never] [font-variant:normal] ic-search-plus w-[44px] h-[44px] flex items-center justify-center absolute right-[5px] top-[5px] z-[2] text-white rounded-full cursor-pointer bg-[rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] hover:bg-[var(--primary)]\"\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\n   \u003cbutton class\u003d\"image lazy-image overflow-hidden photo block leading-[0] cursor-pointer text-center opacity-0\" style\u003d\"width:625px;height:416px\"\u003e\n    \u003cpicture\u003e\n     \u003csource srcset\u003d\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw\u003d\u003d\" type\u003d\"image/avif\"\u003e\u003c/source\u003e\n     \u003csource srcset\u003d\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw\u003d\u003d\" type\u003d\"image/webp\"\u003e\u003c/source\u003e\n     \u003cimg src\u003d\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw\u003d\u003d\" alt\u003d\"Cựu Ph\u0026oacute; Tổng thống Mỹ Kamala Harris. Ảnh: NYT\" width\u003d\"625\" height\u003d\"416\" /\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text media-caption text-center text-[18px] leading-[24px]\"\u003e\u003cem\u003eCựu Ph\u0026oacute; Tổng thống Mỹ Kamala Harris. Ảnh: NYT\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003e\u0026quot;Nếu t\u0026ocirc;i nghe theo c\u0026aacute;c cuộc khảo s\u0026aacute;t th\u0026igrave; t\u0026ocirc;i đ\u0026atilde; kh\u0026ocirc;ng trở th\u0026agrave;nh Ph\u0026oacute; Tổng thống, v\u0026agrave; t\u0026ocirc;i cũng sẽ kh\u0026ocirc;ng ngồi ở đ\u0026acirc;y\u0026quot;, b\u0026agrave; Harris cho biết.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003eCũng trong cuộc phỏng vấn, cựu Ph\u0026oacute; Tổng thống Mỹ khẳng định những đứa c\u0026ocirc; ch\u0026aacute;u g\u0026aacute;i của b\u0026agrave; \u0026quot;chắc chắn sẽ được chứng kiến một nữ Tổng thống Mỹ\u0026quot;. Khi được hỏi rằng liệu người đ\u0026oacute; c\u0026oacute; thể l\u0026agrave; b\u0026agrave; hay kh\u0026ocirc;ng, b\u0026agrave; Harris đ\u0026aacute;p: \u0026quot;Ho\u0026agrave;n to\u0026agrave;n c\u0026oacute; thể\u0026quot;.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003eVề ph\u0026iacute;a ch\u0026iacute;nh quyền Tổng thống Mỹ Donald Trump, Nh\u0026agrave; Trắng cho rằng b\u0026agrave; Harris n\u0026ecirc;n nhận ra c\u0026aacute;c dấu hiệu từ thất bại trong cuộc bầu cử năm ngo\u0026aacute;i.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003e\u0026quot;Khi thua một c\u0026aacute;ch \u0026aacute;p đảo trong cuộc bầu cử năm 2024, b\u0026agrave; Harris n\u0026ecirc;n hiểu rằng người d\u0026acirc;n Mỹ đ\u0026atilde; kh\u0026ocirc;ng c\u0026ograve;n quan t\u0026acirc;m đến những lời n\u0026oacute;i dối v\u0026ocirc; l\u0026yacute;\u0026quot;, một ph\u0026aacute;t ng\u0026ocirc;n vi\u0026ecirc;n Nh\u0026agrave; Trắng n\u0026oacute;i.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text body-author text-right\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e Việt Dũng \u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n \u003c/div\u003e\n \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp\" tabindex\u003d\"-1\" role\u003d\"dialog\" aria-hidden\u003d\"true\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__bg\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__scroll-wrap\"\u003e\n   \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__container\"\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__item\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__item\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__item\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n   \u003c/div\u003e\n   \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__ui pswp__ui--hidden\"\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__top-bar\"\u003e\n     \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__counter\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n     \u003cbutton type\u003d\"button\" class\u003d\"pswp__button pswp__button--close\" title\u003d\"Close (Esc)\"\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\n     \u003cbutton type\u003d\"button\" class\u003d\"pswp__button pswp__button--share\" title\u003d\"Share\"\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\n     \u003cbutton type\u003d\"button\" class\u003d\"pswp__button pswp__button--fs\" title\u003d\"Toggle fullscreen\"\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\n     \u003cbutton type\u003d\"button\" class\u003d\"pswp__button pswp__button--zoom\" title\u003d\"Zoom in/out\"\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\n     \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__p